  <h2>Synopsis</h2>
  <p>This drama imitates, or in better words, is a spinoff of Romeo and Juliet. It is incredibly entertaining and shows the forbidden love of two individuals. </p>
  <h2>Review</h2>
  <p>Honestly, if you like some drama and romance, then this is the perfect show for you to watch! I have seen many, many modern-day Romeo and Juliet spin-offs, which is by far the best! The romance involved, the feelings that the viewer experiences are all fantastic works of the creator! </p>
